I know some bugs, but the map is still fun.

T has 4 driveable cars and 1 plane
CT can destroy the cars and the plane.

The mission for T is to destroy CT with an explosion button and kill them as traditionally.

The mission for CT is to kill all T before they reach the explosion button.

The two glass room are places where CT can stand and survive the explosion.

In the beginning CTÂ´s need to press at a invisible button (it is straight forward, towards T.). After some seconds CT can walk free within they hallway. 

At the right side it is boost towards T and at left it is at the other direction.



If you want to edit the map send me a pm.
